20
00:02:00,747 --> 00:02:05,387
Young Hero Yue and Miss Yue were chosen by the Hengdao Sect to kill Zhu Yu.

21
00:02:05,387 --> 00:02:07,286
Yes.

22
00:02:07,286 --> 00:02:10,626
I've never appreciated the Hengdao Sect's approach.

23
00:02:10,626 --> 00:02:13,066
But Qi made her choice.

24
00:02:13,066 --> 00:02:15,666
I'm going to stand by her.

25
00:02:15,666 --> 00:02:21,347
I truly admire your lofty spirit.

26
00:02:22,226 --> 00:02:24,867
Alliance Leader Zuo, I bet you know that

27
00:02:24,867 --> 00:02:28,806
Zhu Yu has been consuming Qiyuan Orbs as if she's out of control.

28
00:02:28,806 --> 00:02:32,926
The Righteous Martial Alliance alone is no match for her.

29
00:02:32,926 --> 00:02:37,066
You only stand a chance if you join hands with us.

30
00:02:37,066 --> 00:02:39,666
Commander Yue, is that a threat?

31
00:02:39,666 --> 00:02:41,986
I'm just stating the facts.

32
00:02:43,666 --> 00:02:46,647
What a pity that our reputation...

33
00:02:48,146 --> 00:02:51,387
should end up disdained because of me.

34
00:02:51,387 --> 00:02:53,747
Leader, it matters more to save lives.

35
00:02:53,747 --> 00:02:57,486
Not many people know that the Hengdao Sect controls the Qiyuan Sect.

36
00:02:57,486 --> 00:03:00,127
All you have to do is keep it a secret.

37
00:03:02,106 --> 00:03:04,226
We may fool others.

38
00:03:04,226 --> 00:03:06,787
But how do we fool ourselves?

39
00:03:06,787 --> 00:03:08,586
You can't.

40
00:03:08,586 --> 00:03:12,247
But it's all about having a clear conscience.

41
00:03:12,787 --> 00:03:15,847
Alliance Leader, death shall be my redemption.

42
00:03:15,847 --> 00:03:18,507
I'll die for the alliance.

43
00:03:18,507 --> 00:03:24,506
To protect our reputation, I can drop out of the alliance to assist them.

44
00:03:28,266 --> 00:03:29,747
All right.

45
00:03:29,747 --> 00:03:31,387
You have backbone.

46
00:03:31,387 --> 00:03:34,546
I'll make you the vanguard.

47
00:03:34,546 --> 00:03:35,906
Thank you, Alliance Leader.

48
00:03:35,906 --> 00:03:37,526
Young Hero Yue.

49
00:03:38,586 --> 00:03:44,186
Please inform Ying Xuwei that I agree...

50
00:03:46,626 --> 00:03:49,347
to work with the Hengdao Sect.

51
00:03:51,186 --> 00:03:53,166
Thank you, Alliance Leader Zuo.

52
00:03:53,166 --> 00:03:54,846
Alliance Leader.

53
00:03:56,186 --> 00:04:00,660
This is purely my decision.

54
00:04:01,507 --> 00:04:05,526
You're only pressured by me to carry out the task.

55
00:04:06,546 --> 00:04:08,067
Later,

56
00:04:09,186 --> 00:04:12,646
I'll make it clear to the people.

57
00:04:12,646 --> 00:04:16,006
 We pledge loyalty to you, Alliance Leader. 

58
00:04:21,507 --> 00:04:23,186
Alliance Leader Zuo.

59
00:04:23,186 --> 00:04:27,226
Once Rehai reaches Buried Wind Plains, Zhu Yu will come.

60
00:04:27,226 --> 00:04:31,807
Then you will handle the Yu Clan on Earth.

61
00:04:31,807 --> 00:04:35,906
Yujie Hub will handle the remnant on the Sea of Clear Skies.

62
00:04:36,667 --> 00:04:37,867
All right.

63
00:04:37,867 --> 00:04:44,027
From now on, I will mobilize all our disciples against Zhu Yu.

64
00:04:54,746 --> 00:04:58,026
Zuo Guanren agreed to work with us?

65
00:04:59,347 --> 00:05:02,746
Yue Jinzhao made a deal with him.

66
00:05:04,667 --> 00:05:06,626
Eldest Brother,

67
00:05:06,626 --> 00:05:08,686
do you regret it?

68
00:05:10,626 --> 00:05:12,386
I know I'm beyond redemption.

69
00:05:12,386 --> 00:05:15,660
All I can do is to save the Six Realms.

70
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:17,780
Excuse me, Commanders.

71
00:05:23,147 --> 00:05:26,667
Something is bothering me.

72
00:05:26,667 --> 00:05:30,986
When did Maiming contact you?

73
00:05:33,347 --> 00:05:35,166
Does it matter?

74
00:05:37,386 --> 00:05:38,986
It matters to me.

75
00:05:38,986 --> 00:05:41,466
Please kindly tell me.

76
00:05:43,507 --> 00:05:46,067
Back in the Luori Village,

77
00:05:46,067 --> 00:05:50,127
when you were asking Qi about Rehai,

78
00:05:50,127 --> 00:05:52,408
my people overheard you.

79
00:05:52,408 --> 00:05:55,987
Then, Eldest Brother visited the Luo family...

80
00:05:56,707 --> 00:05:59,247
and spoke with Luo Maiming.

81
00:05:59,247 --> 00:06:01,546
- Luo Maiming was a smart guy. 
  - I hope... 

82
00:06:01,546 --> 00:06:05,707
- He assessed the situation and made a deal with us. 
  - we can work well together. 

83
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:12,761
 This is... the key ring of Rehai? 

84
00:06:15,306 --> 00:06:20,466
 This key ring of Rehai is an important item against Zhu Yu. 

85
00:06:20,466 --> 00:06:26,226
 Next time we meet, we'll discuss how to deal with Zhu Yu. 

86
00:06:26,226 --> 00:06:29,787
 I've agreed to side with you against Zhu Yu. 

87
00:06:29,787 --> 00:06:36,391
 In exchange, shouldn't you show me some sincerity, Commander Ying? 

88
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:41,000
 I wonder if the way to remove the binding shows enough sincerity. 

89
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,040
 I wonder if the way to remove the binding shows enough sincerity. 

90
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,440
We teamed up against Zhu Yu.

91
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:50,979
He did it to learn how to remove the Bloodbinding spell.

92
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,799
Thank you.

93
00:06:57,799 --> 00:06:59,580
No problem.

94
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:18,799
I always thought that Maiming had committed heinous crimes.

95
00:07:18,799 --> 00:07:20,720
I dare not even...

96
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:24,359
think about him these days.

97
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:32,480
But now, I know that he's done his part to help take down Zhu Yu,

98
00:07:34,839 --> 00:07:38,380
I... don't know what to think.

99
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,739
If you're confused,

100
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:50,220
just follow your heart.

101
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:54,600
Think about your initial aspiration.

102
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:57,599
It may offer you the courage to face it.

103
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:03,180
My initial aspiration?

104
00:08:18,239 --> 00:08:21,419
Eldest Brother, have some tea.

105
00:08:25,947 --> 00:08:27,947
What's wrong?

106
00:08:27,947 --> 00:08:30,307
I talked too much?

107
00:08:33,466 --> 00:08:35,667
I know you're soft.

108
00:08:37,186 --> 00:08:41,466
If Zuo Guanren acts according to the plan,

109
00:08:41,466 --> 00:08:44,167
we have a greater chance.

110
00:08:47,426 --> 00:08:50,107
There's only one final step.

111
00:08:50,107 --> 00:08:56,326
With Qi and Yue Jinzhao excluded, four people can approach the Yu Clan.

112
00:08:57,205 --> 00:09:00,966
If we keep our promise to Luo Maiming,

113
00:09:00,966 --> 00:09:04,947
Luo Zhaoyan and Xian Qing are excluded.

114
00:09:04,947 --> 00:09:06,907
As for the remaining two...

115
00:09:08,586 --> 00:09:15,626
Ju Shifang and Shuo Xuan seem to have something going on.

116
00:09:17,466 --> 00:09:21,486
If anything goes wrong, we will do it ourselves.

117
00:09:21,486 --> 00:09:25,590
We must send the removal method of the Bloodbinding to Mist Soul

118
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:27,580
no matter what.

119
00:09:28,347 --> 00:09:30,667
For some people,

120
00:09:30,667 --> 00:09:35,327
the safety of one person matters more than anything.

121
00:09:35,327 --> 00:09:38,466
Before, I didn't believe it.

122
00:09:44,787 --> 00:09:46,227
Eldest Brother,

123
00:09:46,987 --> 00:09:49,126
I've been thinking.

124
00:09:49,126 --> 00:09:51,827
Once the war is over,

125
00:09:51,827 --> 00:09:57,747
let's take Xiaoyuan to travel to the Mortal Realm.

126
00:10:03,746 --> 00:10:05,267
All right.

127
00:10:52,187 --> 00:10:53,667
Xian Qing.

128
00:11:00,427 --> 00:11:03,520
Are you practicing for the battle tomorrow?

129
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:07,154
Yes. Shall we exchange a few moves?

130
00:11:15,307 --> 00:11:16,747
All right.

