♫  This destined path is full of turbulence, but it doesn't matter, watch me forge ahead  ♫

150
00:12:46,648 --> 00:12:52,798
♫  I wander around, writing an immortal legend  ♫

151
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:05,335
♫  So carefree  ♫

152
00:13:05,335 --> 00:13:12,599
♫  Even if the stars fade away, I'll still be waiting  ♫

153
00:13:12,599 --> 00:13:15,995
♫  Unable to forget your gentle look  ♫

154
00:13:15,995 --> 00:13:21,303
♫  Between heaven and earth, I travel the world with my sword in hand  ♫

155
00:13:21,303 --> 00:13:26,527
♫  In the end, gratitude and revenge have all been forgotten  ♫

156
00:13:26,527 --> 00:13:28,586
Want a break?

157
00:13:30,906 --> 00:13:32,427
All right.

158
00:13:40,561 --> 00:13:45,207
It seems that your mindset changed just now.

159
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:53,607
You told me to keep my initial aspiration.

160
00:13:53,607 --> 00:13:55,566
I've been thinking...

161
00:13:56,527 --> 00:14:00,286
and I finally figured it out during our practice.

162
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:05,886
It's my aspiration and obligation to shoulder my duty

163
00:14:05,886 --> 00:14:09,386
and protect the people I care about.

164
00:14:15,347 --> 00:14:18,167
You have a great ambition.

165
00:14:18,167 --> 00:14:20,146
I will stand by you.

166
00:14:21,987 --> 00:14:24,606
I can die for anyone,

167
00:14:26,987 --> 00:14:29,447
but I only live for one person.

168
00:14:44,107 --> 00:14:47,767
Commander Ge, I've learned a lot about gadgets from you these days.

169
00:14:47,767 --> 00:14:48,747
Thanks.

170
00:14:48,747 --> 00:14:50,206
No problem.

171
00:14:50,206 --> 00:14:51,787
Oh, right.

172
00:14:52,466 --> 00:14:55,586
Thanks to your instructions,

173
00:14:55,586 --> 00:14:58,007
I've managed to improve it.

174
00:14:58,007 --> 00:14:59,360
 Shifang! 

175
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,920
Coming.

176
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,647
Commander Ge, Jinzhao is calling me.

177
00:15:03,647 --> 00:15:05,547
See you.

178
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,867
Go ahead.

179
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:17,166
Goodbye...

180
00:15:17,747 --> 00:15:20,207
and farewell.

181
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:36,090
   

182
00:15:36,090 --> 00:15:38,630
   

183
00:15:59,307 --> 00:16:00,627
Alliance Leader Zuo.

184
00:16:00,627 --> 00:16:02,447
How did it go?

185
00:16:03,066 --> 00:16:08,466
Chen Qianjun and our people were spotted by the demons at Buried Wind Plains

186
00:16:08,466 --> 00:16:10,887
and suffered a huge loss.

187
00:16:10,887 --> 00:16:15,127
The battle hasn't started and we are already suffering huge losses?

188
00:16:15,127 --> 00:16:18,867
Alliance Leader Zuo, please do me a favor.

189
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:24,326
The gadgets of Yujie Hub can attack the physical form of Kun.

190
00:16:24,326 --> 00:16:26,007
But it's a mythical beast.

191
00:16:26,007 --> 00:16:29,567
The attack has to land on the weakest spot to work.

192
00:16:29,567 --> 00:16:31,946
Commander Ying has observed Zhu Yu for years

193
00:16:31,946 --> 00:16:36,787
and came up with three possible weak spots. However, they aren't certain.

194
00:16:36,787 --> 00:16:41,507
The stored energy allows the Yujie Hub to launch three attacks.

195
00:16:42,427 --> 00:16:45,606
The Hengdao Sect needs the Dragon Crystals in Wuyan Village.

196
00:16:45,606 --> 00:16:49,867
The more crystals we dig out, the more likely we can win.

197
00:16:49,867 --> 00:16:52,627
I thought the Hengdao Sect could see the future

198
00:16:52,627 --> 00:16:54,787
and had an awe-inspiring power.

199
00:16:54,787 --> 00:16:57,567
In the end, they need us to dig rocks for them.

200
00:16:57,567 --> 00:16:59,280
Lingyun.

201
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:00,966
 See the future? 

202
00:17:00,966 --> 00:17:04,447
We're not doing this for the Hengdao Sect or the Yujie Hub.

203
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:08,066
It's for the people in this world.

204
00:17:08,066 --> 00:17:09,266
That's right.

205
00:17:09,266 --> 00:17:12,806
To fight for the people is to fight for ourselves.

206
00:17:16,320 --> 00:17:20,287
Miss Yue, you're truly wise.

207
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:25,227
Lingyun, make the arrangements.

208
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:27,363
Understood.

209
00:17:29,586 --> 00:17:31,827
Where is Shifang?

210
00:17:31,827 --> 00:17:35,287
He went to check on the gadgets at the Mechanic Skill Hall.

211
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:40,347
It's his birthday.

212
00:17:41,146 --> 00:17:43,267
Never mind.

213
00:17:43,267 --> 00:17:46,566
Get to business.

214
00:18:57,466 --> 00:18:59,107
Come in.

215
00:19:02,627 --> 00:19:04,847
Senior Xian Qing?

216
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:27,707
   

217
00:19:40,887 --> 00:19:45,247
 I've entrusted the way to undermine Zhu Yu to someone trustworthy. 

218
00:19:45,247 --> 00:19:51,227
 Come at 13:15 to the river shore of Jing'an if you're interested. 

219
00:20:02,255 --> 00:20:04,035
   

220
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:14,410
   

221
00:20:34,786 --> 00:20:36,427
Is anyone here?

222
00:20:46,227 --> 00:20:47,827
Is anyone here?

223
00:20:56,786 --> 00:20:58,466
Cang Feng?

224
00:20:58,466 --> 00:21:00,727
You delivered the letter?

225
00:21:02,747 --> 00:21:04,347
Then Miss Ming...

226
00:21:04,347 --> 00:21:07,106
I asked her to meet me tomorrow.

227
00:21:09,107 --> 00:21:10,267
    
 The note said

228
00:21:10,267 --> 00:21:12,627
if I was ready to sacrifice myself,

229
00:21:12,627 --> 00:21:15,307
you could help us undermine Kun's power.

230
00:21:17,387 --> 00:21:19,175
It's from my master.

231
00:21:23,071 --> 00:21:25,487
 The bottle contains Yue Qi's blood. 

232
00:21:25,487 --> 00:21:28,326
 Yue Qi and Zhu Yu are bonded by blood. 

233
00:21:28,326 --> 00:21:32,000
 Her blood is the key to removing the Bloodbinding. 

234
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:36,481
 Smudge the blood on Shuo Xuan and injure her 

235
00:21:36,481 --> 00:21:40,487
 so that she enters the Core of the Demon Realm for treatment. 

236
00:21:40,487 --> 00:21:43,260
 Yue Qi's blood and the power of Rehai 

237
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:48,600
 will remove the Bloodbinding between Zhu Yu and Mist Soul. 

238
00:21:49,547 --> 00:21:54,280
 Zhu Yu's Vitality Energy will decrease rapidly 

239
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:57,546
 and that's your best chance to kill her. 

240
00:21:57,546 --> 00:22:00,340
M-Miss Shuo Xuan?

241
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:03,740
Does it have to be her?

242
00:22:03,740 --> 00:22:05,227
Yes.

243
00:22:09,427 --> 00:22:11,047
Shuo...

244
00:22:11,650 --> 00:22:13,570
Shuo...

245
00:22:14,711 --> 00:22:16,352
You're hesitating.

246
00:22:16,352 --> 00:22:19,934
If you're scared, forget it.

247
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:31,166
I didn't know it was Shifang's birthday.

248
00:22:31,166 --> 00:22:34,006
He never mentioned it.

249
00:22:34,786 --> 00:22:38,766
After today, Young Shifang will be one year older.

250
00:22:39,426 --> 00:22:42,586
Alliance Leader Zuo and Commander Ying were discussing the battle earlier.

251
00:22:42,586 --> 00:22:45,767
It sounded like Alliance Leader Zuo wanted to celebrate Shifang's birthday.

252
00:22:45,767 --> 00:22:48,867
But he may not have time for it.

253
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:55,546
When we toured around Jing'an at night, I think he mentioned that

254
00:22:55,546 --> 00:23:00,107
he would love to celebrate his birthday just like Ming Xiu did.

255
00:23:03,426 --> 00:23:05,926
